title: Băncile canadiene scad dobânzile la cărțile de credit. Cine poate beneficia de această decizie?
content: I’ve been working with Canada’s banks to ensure they support customers impacted by COVID-19 I’m pleased to share that @CIBC , @RBC & @nationalbank are taking action to lower credit card rates, and I hope more banks will soon follow. pic.twitter.com/5Wde9noZ5Z
